{"tid":1961626,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【SARS後遺症】嗅覺一去不返 台護士遺憾再聞不到香水味：至少還活着","createTime":"2020-04-07T02:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T11:09:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"280fe7c9944868d2df8d3e2300dba676170e38ca","tid":1961626,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"「染煞（SARS）後，我的嗅覺忽然沒了，連最喜歡的香水味也聞不到了！」台灣台北市立聯合醫院和平院區急症室護士楊大音，17年前因感染SARS住院，出院後居家隔離，在刷牙時突然發現聞不到牙膏的薄荷味，從此嗅覺再沒有恢復，如今眼見武漢肺炎感染者亦有味覺、嗅覺異常，讓她深感憂心，也期盼她的酸楚不會發生在別人身上。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情蔓延，除咳嗽、發燒等症狀外，許多病人味覺、嗅覺異常，台中央流行疫情指揮中心已於4月1日正式新增通報定義，只要味覺、嗅覺異常，即可視為武漢肺炎疑似個案通報並採檢，而依指揮中心統計，截至4月5日共確診363人，當中有39人出現味覺、嗅覺異常，比例近17%。<br />\n<br />\n嚴峻的疫情，加上患者味覺、嗅覺異常，讓楊大音百感交集。她說，SARS爆發時，她是和平醫院（現為北市聯醫和平院區）急症室護士，在封院前幾天，她開始發燒、咳嗽，雖前往診所看病，但醫生一聽到她是和平醫院護士，都不願替她看診，還要求她回和平醫院就醫，「沒想到一回院就遇上封院」。<br />\n<br />\n楊大音看着遠方，回想當時心情，「住院期間，我每天都很煎熬」，看着電視播報全是醫護人員殉職消息，包括護士長陳靜秋等，內心很不好受，最後乾脆鎖定電影台，但內心巨大壓力仍揮之不去。她哽咽說：「當時很悲觀，害怕會死掉，甚至會想輕生。」後來又發現自己的記憶力減退，有些事無法想起，結果醫生證實，她是因壓力過大引起創傷壓力症候群，且損及大腦海馬體，影響記憶力，而更讓她難過的是，她至今仍自覺記憶力沒完全恢復，「現在和老公聊天，會發現很多發生的事都想不起來」。<br />\n不過，楊大音的不幸不止於此，當年她在和平醫院住滿14天出院後就居家隔離，未料第三天早上刷牙時，她突然驚覺聞不到牙膏的薄荷味，即使換了牙膏，仍聞不出味道，同時還出現了發燒、腹瀉等症狀，便再次就醫。她經救護車送至台北市婦幼醫院（現為北市聯醫婦幼院區），接診醫生說：「你說聞不到，但現在誰敢看你的鼻子？」結果根本沒有為她治療。至於腹瀉症狀，「感覺像無止境的狂瀉」，一天肚屙6至7次，幾乎快脫水，後來禁食4天且不斷補充葡萄糖、水分、電解質等，才慢慢止瀉。<br />\n<br />\n這次住院讓楊大音確認染疫導致她失去嗅覺。她當時十分惱怒，「覺得好像甚麼事都不能做了」、「人生就這樣了」。有次她在家裏煮水，水燒開很久，水壺的塑膠蓋都被熱到融化，她卻完全沒聞到焦味，當時發現後，想到自己真的沒了嗅覺，感到非常難過，甚至遷怒媽媽：「像吃飯的時候，我就會抱怨都已經聞不到菜香了，難道菜色不能做好看一點嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n如此低潮持續2、3年後，楊大音的心情才逐漸平復，「我慶幸至少還活着，只是生活少了一樣（嗅覺）」。她也說，記得那時染疫失去嗅覺的患者不只她，應該還有2人。<br />\n<br />\n最近楊大音看到越來越多武漢肺炎患者失去嗅覺、味覺，十分擔心，她感覺病毒在變異，呼籲民眾一察覺聞不到、吃不出味道，就應趕快接受篩檢。她以過來人身份說，剛失去嗅覺時四處求醫，希望能盡快恢復，曾有耳鼻喉科醫生告訴她，可以多聞一些有獨特味道的東西，例如咖啡豆、士多啤梨、香水等，像她就拿咖啡豆當指標，「想像一打開咖啡店的門，就會聞到濃郁的咖啡香」，但這心願一直沒有實現。<br />\n<br />\n然而，相較於咖啡，其實失去嗅覺後讓楊大音最難割捨的，其實是香水，「聞不到真的好遺憾，但看到喜歡的還是會買，不想放棄這美好的事情。」對於已遺忘的許多SARS回憶，她說，不好的事情就關在小房間裏面，不去碰觸，也不必去想起。<br />\n<br />\n楊大音的身體慢慢康復後，決定還是回到和平醫院工作，而且繼續擔任急症室護士，「沒有辦法，我還是很喜歡護士的工作呢！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200406/large/1586173578_022b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200406%2Flarge%2F1586173578_022b.jpg&h=3f0c4c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200407/FZ4E5X5UKMBPTHHAQ4U2LLF5QU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200407%2FFZ4E5X5UKMBPTHHAQ4U2LLF5QU%2F&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=5f30e434\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200407%2FFZ4E5X5UKMBPTHHAQ4U2LLF5QU%2F&h=57a3bab5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200407/FZ4E5X5UKMBPTHHAQ4U2LLF5QU/</a>"},{"pid":"ba07e748238d67f4268fc3e5bc169d2482161ffc","tid":1961626,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:23:11.000Z","msg":"病毒破壞嗅覺神經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947c5283b904c29c724eb1297fffd2f7c5dac5ea","tid":1961626,"uid":346806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:24:38.000Z","msg":"真係好慘...<br />\n唔怪得台灣咁認真去處理<br />\n香港仲慘，但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e722358b9a0741d63d85cb7aaff58066a8fe4fb","tid":1961626,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"947c5283b904c29c724eb1297fffd2f7c5dac5ea","tid":1961626,"uid":346806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:24:38.000Z","msg":"真係好慘...<br />\n唔怪得台灣咁認真去處理<br />\n香港仲慘，但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"以前董太都識得叫人洗手，香港政府而家仲衰過沙士果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64265df25e000f625d71ad7d6c8be814b4b90474","tid":1961626,"uid":19485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e722358b9a0741d63d85cb7aaff58066a8fe4fb","tid":1961626,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"947c5283b904c29c724eb1297fffd2f7c5dac5ea","tid":1961626,"uid":346806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:24:38.000Z","msg":"真係好慘...<br />\n唔怪得台灣咁認真去處理<br />\n香港仲慘，但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"以前董太都識得叫人洗手，香港政府而家仲衰過沙士果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:55:08.000Z","msg":"真係一代不如一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班特首高官<br />\n第一個都唔係好，點諗到第4代仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850f5bf8f3c1f41f705aac8ad74f572ee5a70d0a","tid":1961626,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"64265df25e000f625d71ad7d6c8be814b4b90474","tid":1961626,"uid":19485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e722358b9a0741d63d85cb7aaff58066a8fe4fb","tid":1961626,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"947c5283b904c29c724eb1297fffd2f7c5dac5ea","tid":1961626,"uid":346806,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:24:38.000Z","msg":"真係好慘...<br />\n唔怪得台灣咁認真去處理<br />\n香港仲慘，但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"以前董太都識得叫人洗手，香港政府而家仲衰過沙士果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:55:08.000Z","msg":"真係一代不如一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班特首高官<br />\n第一個都唔係好，點諗到第4代仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"其實係，不過真係完全冇諗過香港經歷過沙士，個政府居然可以衰過果陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5488814d3ba4a672913221f283b46ac7385a63b4","tid":1961626,"uid":123308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:46:23.000Z","msg":"新冠病毒或侵害神經系統損害大腦 仍需進一步研究<br />\n2020年4月2日 14:24<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多個國家都發現，有感染新型冠狀病毒的患者出現頭痛、癲癇，甚至精神錯亂等神經系統症狀。有專家認為，病毒有可能直接入侵大腦，令腦部受損</span></span>，但強調仍需進一步研究才能下結論。<br />\n<br />\n隨着新冠病毒全球大流行，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">患者不只出現跟流感相似的病徵，還有部分人失去味覺和嗅覺，甚至更加嚴重</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n美國其中一個患者是一名74歲男人，本身長期病患。他上月初因為發燒和咳嗽求診，原先醫院為他照X光後，排除他有肺炎，讓他回家；但翌日他持續發高燒，家人將他送回醫院。他一度呼吸困難和說不出話，加上手腳不由自主地抽搐，似乎癲癇發作。醫生為他做測試，確診感染新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n另一宗個案是一名50多歲航空公司女職員。她向醫生表示感到迷迷糊糊和頭痛，除了自己的名字，她當時能提供的個人資訊不多，而且反應越見遲緩。腦掃瞄顯示，她腦內出現腫脹和發炎，更加有細胞壞死。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有神經系統專家認為，這顯示病毒會直接入侵人的大腦，造成急性壞死性腦病變的罕有併發症</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n內地早前有研究發現，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新冠病毒會攻擊大腦中樞神經以至周圍的神經系統，超過三成新冠患者會出現神經系統症狀，包括面癱和出現幻覺等，嚴重的更可能有急性腦血管疾病</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">類似的病例在德國、法國、奧地利、荷蘭和意大利都有出現；意大利北部有醫院更專門成立小組，治療新冠病毒併發腦病變的病人，當中有患者曾出現中風、癲癇和類似腦炎的症狀，部分人甚至精神錯亂</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n不過，專家同時指出，新冠病毒對神經系統到底造成怎樣的影響仍需進一步的研究，目前任何斷言仍是言之尚早；又強調大部分新冠患者的神經功能都屬正常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=386462\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D386462&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le%2Fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=4d076a0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D386462&h=fd8acc37\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=386462</a>"},{"pid":"3f93c9fb4606f973bc37c7b48aa190482e035691","tid":1961626,"uid":168911,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"WTF，原來係永久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd4cd3b4d36f0679d67fe56204be68ad06fd8ce","tid":1961626,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f93c9fb4606f973bc37c7b48aa190482e035691","tid":1961626,"uid":168911,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"WTF，原來係永久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:02:15.000Z","msg":"你以為感冒啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0072da7a1fd0b3e4a9fcfb759f39668b855576","tid":1961626,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:04:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"524d779d0948068eb41775b214634acedf4a49a8","tid":1961626,"uid":220304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"好慘&hellip;&hellip;咁就一世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等啲人仲響度掉以輕心，以為傷風感冒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d351b0d8533084891b3beb092baf8e74f1fe3cca","tid":1961626,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:40:36.000Z","msg":"進化緊做喪屍病毒咁"},{"pid":"ca1e951d5e0dd04aa65130034f4db2d6a3cb9859","tid":1961626,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"524d779d0948068eb41775b214634acedf4a49a8","tid":1961626,"uid":220304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"好慘&hellip;&hellip;咁就一世 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等啲人仲響度掉以輕心，以為傷風感冒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲周街去果d人，中左招真係完全唔抵可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}